<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Renfrew</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A purely residential area in this part of the city, the community in Renfrew is one of the most desirable neighborhoods in the whole of Calgary.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">Often touted as a hidden gem the Renfrew real estate offers homebuyers a great quality of life at an irresistible pricing.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The neighborhood is surrounded by the Deerfoot Trail and the Nose Hill Creek on the east and the Edmonton Trail on the west.</p>

